title: Kingdom Hearts Quiz
content: If you are a huge nerd that loves Kingdom Hearts then try your knowledge on the quiz. Even the most experienced players will fumble on some questions. Careful with how you answer, you lose 5 seconds every time you get something wrong.

title: Password Generator
content: Will create a password for you based on the criteria you choose! Choose from lowercase, uppercase, special characters and character length to create your own secure password.

title: Interactive State Map
content: This map will show you all of the sex education laws in the United States in 2021.
